title: $TEAK APR-M on Polygon
body:
[See the proposal on forum](https://kangaltoken.community/t/proposal-discussion-incentivized-apr-m-on-polygon/232)

Option 1: Set Polygon $TEAK APR-M to 35% to incentivize staking on Polygon
Option 2: Set Polygon $TEAK APR-M to 30%, same as BSC
author: 0x63c67Ba2aa323e47eddDB3952990CF41768a679c
